  "text": "The goal of this section is to evaluate the performance of the proposed algorithms. Simulation results are obtained by averaging 1000 independent random network realizations. The users are uniformly distributed within a circle with radius of 10m. The attenuation of the links considering large-scale statistics are determined using the path loss model given by 8: if t u = 0 then [CITATION_1] . The self interference coefficient β is taken as −70 dBm.",
